Subject: [PATCH] ALSA/ASoC: hda: move/rename snd_hdac_ext_stop_streams to hdac_stream.c
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 12054f0ce8be7d2003ec068ab27c9eb608397b98
Patch-mainline: v5.17-rc1
